title: Wesli - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Wesli performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded June 20, 2023

Songs:
Latibonit
Doudou
Mon Konpè
Eya hé/Rara

Wesley Louissaint - Vocals, Guitar, Congas
Cindy Belotte - Vocals, Dance
Watson Joseph - Bass
Michel Medrano Brindis - Drums
David Mobio - Keyboards
André Désilets - Sax, Flute, Vocals, Hand percussion
Martine Labbé - Percussion
Trumpet, Back vocals, Hand percussion

Host: Gabriel Teodros
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs
Audio Mixer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
